title: Independent candidate Sharafat Ali wins PK-3 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Independent candidate Sharafat Ali has won the Khyber Pakhtunkhwa Assembly election from PK-3 Swat-I by securing 25,170 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was PML-N’s Jehangir who bagged 11, 774 votes.
Voters’ turn-out remained 32.73 percent.
